      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "His blood    work revealed a lactate of 7.5, an LDH of 2635 and an AG acidosis.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row447958#s6",
      "text": "His blood    work revealed a lactate of 7.5, an LDH of 2635 and an AG acidosis."
    },
    {
